features: 【ECO FRIENDLY 】 100% Bamboo. A sustainable and environmentally friendly option that produces 65.5% fewer emissions as compared to traditional tissue materials
【NO BLEACH or FLUORESCENTS USED】Made purely from 100% natural bamboo fibers without any whitening chemicals (Naturally hypoallergenic free from chemicals)

【Absorbent】 Each 3 Ply tissue is extremely moisture absorbent (25% more absorbent than regular wood pulp tissues), strong and tear resistant. The fibers do not separate or leave paper residue or paper scraps on the skin when used, even when wet
【FOR YOU & FOR THE PLANET】 Use bamboo tissue for the whole family, in and around the house, in the car. Fits easily in your purse or school bag
body.description: Why use bamboo facial tissue ? This facial tissues are made of unbleached pure natural bamboo fibers and bamboo pulp, without additives, fluorescent whiteners or bleach. The tissues are absolutely safe and convenient to use for the whole family including pregnant women and babies. This bamboo fibers are eco-friendly and certified for sustainable forest harvest. DELLBOO production and harvest practices help reduce deforestation, environmental pollution and promote eco-friendly consumption PLANET FRIENDLY - Bamboo is grown without chemical fertilizers or irrigation, and reduce up to 35% of the carbon dioxide in the air. 51,000 trees used daily to meet the demand of single-use paper towels, making it unsustainable in the long run

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Smaller Than Regular Tissues
reviews.reviewText: These tissues are soft & feel like regular bleached tissues that have all the chemicals in them but they are waaayyy smaller. (See pictures attached). I read many of the reviews before I purchased so I knew they were smaller but none of the reviews said they were so small they were the size of the pocket packs of Kleenex. I have smaller than normal hands & in the picture you can see the size of the tissue compared to my hand. I really wish they could make these in a size comparable to a regular size tissue. If you’re using them to blow your nose, you only get 1 blow/tissue. Disappointed, will not purchase again.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Too-Small Tissues Are Not Soft
reviews.reviewText: These tissues are 2-ply but they're also half the size of other tissues. This is like a size you get in a sample pack of something you didn't want in the first place. I opened up one of the packs to see if I would like them, so they are no longer returnable.I'm a big fan of bamboo products but I expected more from these. I can buy a regular size tissue, 2 ply, qty 210 for less than what each package of these would cost individually.Not worth it at all.
